oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Joe King Publicity Photo
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: King, Joe;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white three-quarter length portrait of Joe King standing outside next to a cat in a tree. The photo was released by King - J Records and Total Concept Rep. Inc. A typed note on the back of the photo says, "November 1981." A handwritten note on the back of the photo says, "60%," presumably in reference to the size of the metal photoplate made from the photo.
